   Search                 View Menu  Down arrow icon            Breadcrumbs   College of Nursing    Programs & Applying    Find Your Program        Find Your Program  If you're looking to begin or advance a nursing career, we've got the right—and the best—program to help you reach your goal.       Programs in brief     Bachelor of Science in Nursing   This is for you if …  You have a high school diploma or some college credit and want to become an RN  or  you are an RN who wants to earn a BSN.  LEARN MORE     Master of Science for non-RNs   This is for you if …  You have a bachelor’s degree in a field other than nursing and want to enter the nursing field at an advanced level.  LEARN MORE     Master of Science for RNs   This is for you if …  You are an RN with a bachelor’s degree in any field and wish to advance your skills with additional education.  LEARN MORE     Doctor of Nursing Practice   This is for you if …  You are an RN with a bachelor’s and/or master’s degree in any field and want to be come and advanced practice nurse (APRN)  or  you are an APRN wishing to obtain certification in a new practice area  or  you are an APRN wishing to earn a clinical doctorate in your current practice area.  LEARN MORE     Doctor of Philosophy   This is for you if …  You are an RN with a bachelor’s or master’s degree in nursing who wants to earn a research-focused doctorate.  LEARN MORE     Certificate Programs   This is for you if …  You are an RN who wishes to advance your education in a specialty area without earning another degree  or  you are an RN with a DNP who wishes to qualify for credentialing in a new practice area.  LEARN MORE         Get all the information you need        Explore any of these programs  Dig into all the information about the program you have your eye on          Attend an info session  View the complete list of upcoming in-person and virtual info sessions at all campuses          Request information  Use this simple form to request that we conta